.TH MFUTIL 1 2025-01-01 "mfutil 0.1.1"
.SH NAME
mfutil \- Music Folder Utils: Organize and manage your music library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mfutil
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.RI [ SUBCOMMAND ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B mfutil
is a comprehensive music library management tool designed to help you organize,
tag, and enhance your music collection. It provides features for extracting album
art, creating symlinks, syncing with MusicBrainz, importing music, and more.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Print help information
.TP
.B \-V, \-\-version
Print version information
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
.B art
Extract album art from music files and fetch from online sources
.TP
.B albums
Create symlinks to album directories for easy access
.TP
.B tracks
Create symlinks to individual track files
.TP
.B sync
Sync music tags with MusicBrainz and fetch cover art
.TP
.B reorganize
Move misplaced music files to their proper artist/album structure
.TP
.B import
Import music files from external directories into your library
.TP
.B cd
Import music directly from audio CDs (requires cd-ripping feature)
.TP
.B all
Run all available tasks (art, icons, albums, tracks, organize)
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B MUSIC_DIR
Default music directory path (defaults to ~/Music)
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/mfutil/
Configuration directory for API keys and settings
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Process album art for your music library:
.B mfutil art
.TP
Create album symlinks:
.B mfutil albums
.TP
Sync tags with MusicBrainz:
.B mfutil sync
.TP
Import music from an external directory:
.B mfutil import /path/to/external/music
.TP
Run all tasks:
.B mfutil all
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR mfutil-art (1),
.BR mfutil-albums (1),
.BR mfutil-tracks (1),
.BR mfutil-sync (1),
.BR mfutil-reorganize (1),
.BR mfutil-import (1),
.BR mfutil-cd (1),
.BR mfutil-all (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Written by the mfutil development team.